{"id": "1505686711403806812", "channel_id": "1505686711403806812", "author_id": "1160510535670968330", "author_name": "yeriko703", "content": "Day 2. Dev still remain silent. Lets share this on q-a \n\nI start playing when clem release i caught the 1.5 anniversary, the drama around it and the subsequent ones.\nAbout character design(hello kath), about raid event, about dupes(how many dupes need), about powercreep(gmurphy), about +12, about skins, about gacha on skins(murphy hello skin), about fomo baners, about paid banner.\n\nAnd you know what I hear all this time? Sorry, we are so sorry and promise, we don't do this again. I'm sure they do this again xd ( https://tenor.com/view/were-sorry-tony-hayward-south-park-s14e11-coon2rise-of-captain-hindsight-gif-22864475 )\n\nMorimens is great game with great story but dev team do mistakes again, again and again. They try to tell us all the time that \"Morimens belongs not only to us but also to you\" but it just doesn't work when you're constantly apologizing and breaking promises.\n\nLight is trying to show that he hears us and is ready to communicate. But the last post in <#1426837316533747823>  was about 2 months ago, <#1180845276823564288>  they take a very long time to respond (you'll be lucky if they respond at all)\n\n1. Cancel 300 normal pull for stats\n\n2. Decide how you'll interact with the community. If you want to continue reaching out to players, it might be better to create occasional Q&A posts\n\n3. Give us road map future plans\n\n4. Stop apologize and do something real, not only words \n\n5. Stop making promises that will eventually be broken anyway", "timestamp": "2026-05-17T21:41:26.305000+00:00", "thread_id": "1505686711403806812", "reactions": [{"emoji": "goliath_spend", "emoji_id": "1468259820875415728", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 13}], "attachments": [{"id": "1505686711634759860", "filename": "130159904_p2_master1200.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 336688, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1505686711403806812/1505686711634759860/130159904_p2_master1200.jpg?ex=6a0c3046&is=6a0adec6&hm=9ac6940e6dfb9578cc80c5f3b479d541d12ac0afe82b0db7152ba25d9bc4c45c&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "gifv", "title": "", "url": "https://tenor.com/view/were-sorry-tony-hayward-south-park-s14e11-coon2rise-of-captain-hindsight-gif-22864475", "description": ""}]}
