{"id": "1505710591908778035", "channel_id": "1505686711403806812", "author_id": "277927692735873035", "author_name": "choco_minnto", "content": "<@1487626955791663208> <@&1166257943742787615> \n\n- why introduce daily banners (unit + wheel combined) when so many players complained back in 2.4 and devs apologised & changed it? \n\n- why put standard unit upgrade behind a 300 pure core wall? previously limited awakeners received a 10% buff to their stats, is it that difficult to give standard units the same 10% stat buff to minimise the power gap?\n\n- why put ethereal cores inside paid $$ half anniversary pack? isn’t ethereal cores used to combat RMT account sellers and only used in special occasion? how does paying for temporary pulls make sense ? \n\n- why put a time-gate on anniversary rewards? players will lose out on daily banners or do you only care about players spending more $$$?", "timestamp": "2026-05-17T23:16:19.861000+00:00", "thread_id": "1505686711403806812", "mentions": ["1487626955791663208"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
